**“Licensed Work”** means the software, source code, binaries, documentation, configuration files, and related materials distributed under this License.

**“Production Use”** means any use of the Licensed Work:
- in a commercial environment,
- for generating revenue,
- for providing services to third parties,
- as part of a SaaS, hosted platform, cloud service, or managed service,
- inside an organization with more than the permitted number of users,
- or in any environment not explicitly permitted under the Additional Use Grant.

**“Source Code”** means the preferred form of the Licensed Work for making modifications.

